1. Idem u prodavnicu. (*prodavnicu*) (I'm going to the store.)
2. Kupio sam kolače u toj prodavnici. (prodavnici) (I bought cakes in that store.)
3. U ovoj prodavnici ima dobra ponuda. (prodavnici) (This store has a good selection.)
4. Prodavnica je bila zatvorena kad sam došao. (*Prodavnica*) (The store was closed when I arrived.)
5. Prodavnica se nalazi na uglu. (*Prodavnica*) (The store is located on the corner.)
6. Radnica u prodavnici je vrlo ljubazna. (prodavnici) (The store employee is very friendly.)
7. Prodavnica se renovira, pa neće raditi neko vreme. (*Prodavnica*) (The store is being renovated and won't be open for a while.)
8. Odem u prodavnicu skoro svaki dan. (*prodavnicu*) (I go to the store almost every day.)
9. Prodavnica prodaje sve vrste voća i povrća. (prodavnici) (The store sells all kinds of fruits and vegetables.)
10. Prodavnica je blizu mog stana. (*Prodavnica*) (The store is close to my apartment.)